":"text","text":", S, Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stuffed her vulva with cotton,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA,) to arrest the blood. (S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHota$ato","text_ar":"اِحْتَشَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy~apF","text_ar":"حَشِيَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHa$iy~apK","text_ar":"بِحَشِيَّةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wore a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy~ap","text_ar":"حَشِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHa$~ato","text_ar":"تَحَشَّتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone]. (Az, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H$Y","text_ar":"حشى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) A poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laA taHota$iY A_il~aA AlS~amiyma AlS~aAdiqaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She will not wear any stuffing but that which is genuine"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"true"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: meaning that she will not wear"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$aAyaA","text_ar":"حَشَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the largeness of her posteriors renders it needless for her to do so. (IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}